room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape The Room Oregon in Eugene
room_description:
You and your group have run out of gas in the woods of the pacific northwest. You stumble upon a cabin. Hoping to find the help, you enter the cabin, only to find it is owned by a paranoid conspiracy theory prepper. He has the whole cabin wired to explode.
You and your group have 60 minutes to solve the puzzles and clues left behind by this madman to get out before the bomb goes off. Do you have what it takes to escape the cabin?
